    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1896-01-16T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1896-01-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="458"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d458">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Manion</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Johannesburg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-01-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 16, 1896</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Impossible report definitely now. Can not comprehend international intrigues.
                    Seven American citizens, all representative, reputable men, under arrest; have
                    officially appointed R. E. Brown, Idaho, prominent, highly respected here, join
                    me in commission investigation all details for purpose of report. Advise firm
                    stand in behalf our citizens, pending full report. This Government is treating
                    prisoners kindly.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Manion</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Consular Agent.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
